PrecisAmendment to the YUKON QUARTZ MINING ACT WORK RELIEF REGULATIONS (1979) extending for a period of two years relief from the legislated work requirements for mineral claim holders in an area of the northern Yukon Territory extending from the Beaufort Sea in the North to the Porcupine and Bell Rivers in the south and from the Alaska to the Northwest Territories boundaries.

precis:
Amendment to the YUKON QUARTZ MINING ACT WORK RELIEF REGULATIONS (1979)
extending for a period of two years relief from the legislated work
requirements for mineral claim holders in an area of the northern Yukon
Territory extending from the Beaufort Sea in the North to the Porcupine
and Bell Rivers in the south and from the Alaska to the Northwest
Territories boundaries.
